    "description": "Jigs4w3D Puzzle Challenge is a casual single-player experience. Chill, enjoy the immersive 3D environments and complete a fine selection of your favourite puzzles. How would that feel solving puzzles generated from your own photos? Search no further and try it out now in the My Photos DLC.<br><br>With this DLC, you can import your own photos and solve procedurally generated puzzles, based on your own images.<br><br>After purchase, a new button will be displayed above the image selection menu. Simply click on the &quot;My Photos&quot; button and browse among your own images. Once you find your favourite photo, choose from 5 difficulty settings and Jigs4w3D Puzzle Challenge procedurally generates a puzzle to solve, in any environment you already have.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><strong>generate your own photos into puzzles to solve</strong><br><br><strong>new, exclusive environment - English Cottage</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034880/extras/422c96a5158d2fb1b959d30920c7cb10.poster.avif?t=1729863443\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034880/extras/422c96a5158d2fb1b959d30920c7cb10.webm?t=1729863443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034880/extras/422c96a5158d2fb1b959d30920c7cb10.mp4?t=1729863443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>enhanced camera movement</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>find small details easily</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3034880/extras/ad8cf96efd9ec45449b24a2624cbc96d.poster.avif?t=1729863443\" width=616 height=136 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i